Package org.opennars.storage

Class Bag<Type extends Item<K>,K>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.opennars.storage.Bag<Type,K>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Iterable<Type>
    public class Bag<Type extends Item<K>,K>
extends Object
implements Serializable, Iterable<Type>
    Original Bag implementation which distributes items into discrete levels (queues) according to priority
    See Also:
